<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-cmn-Hans">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport"
        content="width=device-width, user-scalable=no, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, minimum-scale=1.0">
  <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge">
  <meta name="HandheldFriendly" content="True" />
  <title>{{meta_title}}</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="{{asset "poppy.css"}}" />
  {{ghost_head}}
</head>
<body class="{{body_class}}">
{{{body}}}
<footer class="site-footer">
  <div class="footer-wrap">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-sm-4">
          <div class="foot-center">
            <h4>友情链接</h4>
            <p>
              <a href="http://www.yanfangxiong.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">严方雄的空间</a>
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-sm-4">
          <div class="foot-center">
            <h4>标签</h4>
            <div class="tag-cloud">
              {{#get "tags" limit="10" include="count.posts" order="count.posts desc" }}
                {{#foreach tags}}
                  <a href="/tag/{{slug}}" class="tag-item">{{name}} ({{count.posts}})</a>
                {{/foreach}}
              {{/get}}
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-sm-4">
          <div class="foot-center">
            <h4>关于</h4>
            <p>沉淀知识，分享生活。<br />这是我的个人博客，记录平时遇到的技术问题和学习到新的知识，分享自己的一些生活、感悟。欢迎大家订阅我的博客，获取第一手动态，共同交流进步。</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="footer-bottom">
  </div>
</footer>
<a href="#" id="backTop">
  {{> "icons/up"}}
</a>
<script src="{{asset "vendor.js"}}"></script>
<script src="{{asset "poppy.js"}}"></script>
{{ghost_foot}}
</body>
</html>